's Me\":\n*{{cite web |script-title=ko:2012\ub144 08\uc6d4 Download Chart |quote=see #70|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=08&hitYear=2012&termGbn=month|work=Gaon Music Chart|publisher=Korea Music Content Industry Association|language=Korean}}\n*{{cite web |script-title=ko:2012\ub144 37\uc8fc\ucc28 Download Chart |quote=see #60|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=37&hitYear=2012&termGbn=week|work=Gaon Music Chart|publisher=Korea Music Content Industry Association|language=Korean}}</ref>\n| ''[[To the Beautiful You (soundtrack)|To the Beautiful You OST]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.naver.com/album/index.nhn?albumId=328730 |script-title=ko:\uc544\ub984\ub2e4\uc6b4 \uadf8\ub300\uc5d0\uac8c OST '\ub098\uc57c (It's Me)' (SBS \uc218\ubaa9\ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8)|date=August 22, 2012|publisher=Naver Music|access-date=August 31, 2018|language=Korean}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align: left;\"| \"{{lang|ko-Hang|\ub450 \ubc88\uc9f8 \uc11c\ub78d}} (The 2nd Drawer)\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/the-2nd-drawer/854922748|title=The 2nd Drawer (From \"The Queen's Classroom\") - Single|date=June 13, 2013|publisher=iTunes Store|access-date=August 31, 2018}}</ref>\n| 2013\n| \u2014 || 76\n|style=\"text-align: left;\"|\n* KOR: 30,346+<ref>{{cite web |script-title=ko:2013\ub144 25\uc8fc\ucc28 Download Chart |quote=see #66|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=25&hitYear=2013&termGbn=week|work=Gaon Music Chart|publisher=Korea Music Content Industry Association|language=Korean}}</ref>\n| ''The Queen's Classroom OST''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.naver.com/album/index.nhn?albumId=391523 |script-title=ko:\ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8 '\uc5ec\uc655\uc758 \uad50\uc2e4' OST (MBC \uc218\ubaa9\ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8)|date=August 19, 2013|publisher=Naver Music|access-date=August 31, 2018